AVERMEDIA TECH said unconsolidated sales
in August fell 41.43% to NT$212,754,000 from NT$363,241,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  8/2011           8/2010
Sales            212,754          363,241    
YOY%             -41.43%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales           1,239,149        2,046,414   
YOY%             -39.45% 
=================================================================
 